text:
Kitesurfing all day, drinking whiskey, and talking to the TV all night: According to Jordan Peele’s impersonation of the 44th president of the United States on Late Night , Obama is leaning real hard into retired life. This Obama isn’t buttoned-up enough to require an anger translator . He’s just Vacation Obama, clothes filled with sand, heart filled with schadenfreude, shoes also probably filled with sand.
